knowledge_panel.description: star fox 64, known as lylat wars in the pal regions, is a 3d rail shooter video game developed by nintendo for the nintendo 64. it is the second installment in the star fox series and a reboot of the original star fox for the super nintendo entertainment system. wikipedia
